title: Little Mermaid 3: Ariel's Beginning Soundtrack
description:
Since there probably won't be any official soundtrack release to this film I decided to make my own. It's pretty good quality and all the songs are here. Here is a list of the songs in the file and the format is .wav:

1. One Misstake
2. Jump In the Line
3. I Remember
4. Dance Club Rhythm
5. One Misstake reprise
6. I Remember reprise
7. Jump in the Line reprise
8. I Will Sing
9. Little Mermaid 3 (the entire sound file from the movie if you want to improve the song files.)

Don't complain too much I'm just an amateur!!!! ;) Enjoy!
